{"tid":775820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"齊估港鐵未來新聞標題","createTime":"2018-08-11T13:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T10:26:01.000Z","uid":194374,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53f3c296e6551a5bf2ef69c3f7f827c9481b33da","tid":775820,"uid":194374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"高機率<br />\n<br />\n1. 港鐵完成調查 地盤今復工<br />\n2. 立會再反對運用特權法 民主派促更深入調查<br />\n3. 完成加固工程 沙中線即將通車<br />\n4. 無懼安全隱患 沙中線終通車<br />\n5. 過百市民迎通車 安全問題反應兩極<br />\n<br />\n中機率<br />\n<br />\n1. 政府通過修例 下調沉降安全標準<br />\n2. 調查報告指港鐵確違規 律政司即將起訴<br />\n3. 獨立工程小組介入 將進行抽樣檢查<br />\n<br />\n低機率<br />\n1. 沙中線全地盤停工 直至完成調查<br />\n2. 廉署今起訴港鐵 禮頓高層<br />\n3. 完成調查報告 馬時亨正式辭職<br />\n4. 陳帆請辭 力保問責機制<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9454454703b771d521d29d0ae3c59b421d5f5da1","tid":775820,"uid":194374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84315c2802b48e0a68b056ec7b3ba24f59c751c5","tid":775820,"uid":33907,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"最底幾個係零機率 唔係低"},{"pid":"e6931e65d8d57a27e8d4512a93b37b6970b183b3","tid":775820,"uid":116836,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"港鐵加價"},{"pid":"7cc933c9694bc4e6351a85ecc5740cf7787a27e3","tid":775820,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4498db3be5d84fb881dcd365704a6a121bcd8b2d","tid":775820,"uid":83582,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e6931e65d8d57a27e8d4512a93b37b6970b183b3","tid":775820,"uid":116836,"l